title: Akakiko
typeOfFood: Ovo, Japanese, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain Japanese food shop, this one is on the 3rd floor of the Passage shopping mall. Offers veggie choices which are labeled, including a variety of maki, sushi, salads, noodles, and one vegan dessert (mochi).
